ttps://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a9a7159d499970c14400377487448cc8_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "89 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610272972"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIsdui36zgkeA4EAMaCDk3ODk3MTE5IK6gj6UGMAA4hghACnIJNjEwMjcyOTcyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1688540938.80445", "card_id": "Q_610238188", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待越来越火的脑洞科技文？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "以前在小说平台，看到最多的就是玄幻类推荐！现在却天天都是《多元宇宙帝国崛起》，《我真没想当救世主啊》、《走进不科学》、《重生之神级学霸》这种脑洞科技文的推荐，有没有大神知道是什么原因呢"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-81e358f0da1b8fe5494e687f2ba7922a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610238188"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Isdui36zgkeA4EAMaCDk3ODg5MjY3IMKSjqUGMAA4UUALcgk2MTAyMzgxODh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1688540938.81285", "card_id": "Q_610431175", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "8 名代表建议「返还企业高管个税」，当地财税部门回应「违反个税立法根本，无法实现」，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "个人所得税改革涉及千家万户，关系百姓切身利益，历来都是热门话题。 据浙江台州温岭市政府网站消息，温岭市财政局、国家税务总局温岭市税务局近期分别答复当地多位人大代表和政协委员关于「返还企业高管及技术专家个人所得税」的建议称：从 2021 年 9 月开始，财政部门已经取消与税收相挂钩的涉企奖补政策；对高收入人群返还个人所得税，违反了共同富裕原则。 国家税务总局温岭市税务局 6 月 16 日答复温岭市人大十七届三次会议潘灵钢、黄宝荣、林安春、张伟、林玉莲、林应傲、包玲霞、郭招芳等 8 名代表《关于返还企业高管及技术专家个人所得税，助推招商引资招人引智的建议》称，从 2021 年 9 月开始，财政部门已经取消与税收相挂钩的涉企奖补政策。此外，个人所得税税法调节的是高收入人群，建议要求对这些个人进行个人所得税返还，违反了个人所得税法立法的根本，违反了共同富裕原则。综上所述，要求对企业高管及技术专家个人所得税进行返还的建议无法实现，敬请谅解。 8 名代表「建议返还企业高管个税」，当地财税部门：违反个税立法根本，无法实现 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d4f40f622d30524aad76d6e3960262d1_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610431175"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Isdui36zgkeA4EAMaCDk3OTMyMjIzIKOik6UGMAA4JEAMcgk2MTA0MzExNzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1688540938.82274", "card_id": "Q_26993363", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 78}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么在中国《攻壳机动队》不如《EVA》有名？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5632da808a36919be4158e163eb87091_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/26993363"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0Isdui36zgkeA4EAMaBzI5ODAzMjcgmauapAUwADjZAUANcggyNjk5MzM2M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1688540938.82787", "card_id": "Q_609811992", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "离开中超后，发展成功的外援都有谁呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "知名转会记者罗马诺确认，上赛季效力于意甲那不勒斯队的韩国中卫金玟哉即将加盟德甲豪门拜仁慕尼黑。据报道，此番拜仁是以支付韩国人 5000 万欧元